introduction: When burlesque performer Lana and her sexually fluid, fun-loving brother Sebastian move to a new city, they hope to have left their dark secret in the shadows. A chance encounter between Lana and her new neighbor Anja sets in motion an unexpectedly twisted web of complications and emotional turmoil that will not only endanger their secret, but also people's lives. Add to the mix Anja's drug-dealing husband Victor and Lana's long-time and now aging partner Frank, and we have the ingredients for the perfect storm. This is a modern day cult classic full of rich characters and loud color, set to a threatening yet deliciously addictive dark pulse.
